data.description: Welcome to this stunning 5-bedroom, 3-bathroom, sprawling 4632 sq ft home nestled in the highly desirable O'Fallon School District. The gourmet kitchen features stainless appliances, granite counters and butler’s pantry that leads into the formal dining room and living room. Work-from-home with an executive main floor office space that provides a quiet retreat. The finished walkout lower level provides family room, bonus room, 5th bedroom and plumbing for future bath. The three-car garage provides ample space for vehicles and storage. Fitness enthusiasts will love the workout room crowned with a soothing sauna. The secluded loft increases versatility and creativity with 4 bedrooms and 2 full baths nearby. Situated on almost a 1/2 acre, the property presents a tranquil sight with its expansive wooded view—the perfect backdrop for a morning cup of coffee or a quiet afternoon with a book. Buyer to verify all information prior to making offer. Close to SAFB, shopping, schools and St Louis.
